WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: hr

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Prevoditelj: Mislav Ante Omazić - EFZG
Recezent: Tilen Pigac - EFZG

00:00:15.260 --> 00:00:18.260
Moja putovanja u Afganistan

00:00:18.260 --> 00:00:21.260
počela su prije puno, puno godina

00:00:21.260 --> 00:00:24.260
na istočnoj granici moje zemlje,

00:00:24.260 --> 00:00:27.260
moje domovine, Poljske.

00:00:27.260 --> 00:00:29.260
Hodala sam kroz šume

00:00:29.260 --> 00:00:33.260
bakinih priča.

00:00:33.260 --> 00:00:38.260
Zemljom u kojoj se na svakom polju krije grob,

00:00:38.260 --> 00:00:40.260
gdje su milijuni ljudi

00:00:40.260 --> 00:00:43.260
deportirani ili ubijeni

00:00:43.260 --> 00:00:46.260
u 20. stoljeću.

00:00:46.260 --> 00:00:48.260
Iza destrukcije,

00:00:48.260 --> 00:00:51.260
našla sam dušu mjesta.

00:00:51.260 --> 00:00:53.260
Upoznala sam skromne ljude.

00:00:53.260 --> 00:00:55.260
Čula njihove molitve

00:00:55.260 --> 00:00:57.260
i jela njihov kruh.

00:00:57.260 --> 00:01:02.260
Onda sam hodala istočno 20 godina --

00:01:02.260 --> 00:01:05.260
od istočne Europe do centralne Azije --

00:01:05.260 --> 00:01:07.260
kroz planine Kavkaza,

00:01:07.260 --> 00:01:09.260
srednjeg Istoka,

00:01:09.260 --> 00:01:11.260
sjeverne Afrike,

00:01:11.260 --> 00:01:13.260
Rusije.

00:01:13.260 --> 00:01:17.260
I stalno sam sretala sve skromnije ljude.

00:01:17.260 --> 00:01:20.260
I dijelila sam njihov kruh i molitve.

00:01:20.260 --> 00:01:23.260
Zato sam otišla u Afganistan.

00:01:23.260 --> 00:01:27.260
Jednog dana, prelazeći most

00:01:27.260 --> 00:01:29.260
preko rijeke Oxus.

00:01:29.260 --> 00:01:31.260
Bila sam sama, pješice.

00:01:31.260 --> 00:01:33.260
I afganistanski vojnik je bio toliko iznenađen što me vidi

00:01:33.260 --> 00:01:36.260
da je zaboravio poštambiljati mi putovnicu.

00:01:36.260 --> 00:01:38.260
Ali mi je dao šalicu čaja.

00:01:38.260 --> 00:01:40.260
I razumjela sam

00:01:40.260 --> 00:01:43.260
da je njegovo iznenađenje bila moja zaštita.

00:01:43.260 --> 00:01:46.260
Tako sam hodala i putovala,

00:01:46.260 --> 00:01:49.260
konjima, jakovima, kaminonima, autostopirajući,

00:01:49.260 --> 00:01:51.260
od iranske granice

00:01:51.260 --> 00:01:56.260
do dna, do ruba Wakhan koridora.

00:01:56.260 --> 00:01:58.260
I na tom putu

00:01:58.260 --> 00:02:05.260
mogla sam pronaći noor, skriveno svjetlo Afganistana.

00:02:05.260 --> 00:02:07.260
Moje jedino oružje

00:02:07.260 --> 00:02:12.260
je bila moja bilježnica i moja Leica.

00:02:12.260 --> 00:02:14.260
Čula sam molitve Sufija --

00:02:14.260 --> 00:02:16.260
skromnih Muslimana

00:02:16.260 --> 00:02:18.260
koje mrze Talibani.

00:02:18.260 --> 00:02:20.260
Skrivena rijeka,

00:02:20.260 --> 00:02:22.260
isprepletena s misticizmom

00:02:22.260 --> 00:02:25.260
od Gibraltara do Indije.

00:02:25.260 --> 00:02:30.260
Džamija u kojoj je poštovani stranac

00:02:30.260 --> 00:02:32.260
okupan blagoslovom

00:02:32.260 --> 00:02:35.260
i suzama,

00:02:35.260 --> 00:02:39.260
i pozdravljen kao poklon.

00:02:39.260 --> 00:02:41.260
Što znamo

00:02:41.260 --> 00:02:43.260
o zemlji i ljudima

00:02:43.260 --> 00:02:46.260
koji se prave da štite,

00:02:46.260 --> 00:02:49.260
sela

00:02:49.260 --> 00:02:51.260
u kojima je jedini lijek

00:02:51.260 --> 00:02:53.260
koji ubija bol i zaustavlja glad

00:02:53.260 --> 00:02:55.260
opijum?

00:02:55.260 --> 00:02:58.260
To su ovisnici o opijumu

00:02:58.260 --> 00:03:01.260
na krovovima Kabula

00:03:01.260 --> 00:03:05.260
10 godina nakon početka našeg rata.

00:03:05.260 --> 00:03:08.260
Ovo su nomadske djevojke

00:03:08.260 --> 00:03:12.260
koje su postale prostitutke za afganistanske poslovnjake.

00:03:12.260 --> 00:03:14.260
Što znamo o ženama

00:03:14.260 --> 00:03:16.260
10 godina nakon rata?

00:03:16.260 --> 00:03:18.260
Obučene u najlonske vrećice,

00:03:18.260 --> 00:03:20.260
proizvedene u Kini,

00:03:20.260 --> 00:03:24.260
s imenom burka.

00:03:24.260 --> 00:03:26.260
Vidjela sam jednog dana

00:03:26.260 --> 00:03:29.260
najveću školu u Afganistanu,

00:03:29.260 --> 00:03:31.260
žensku školu.

00:03:31.260 --> 00:03:34.260
13.000 cura

00:03:34.260 --> 00:03:38.260
studira ovdje

00:03:38.260 --> 00:03:41.260
u podzemnim sobama,

00:03:41.260 --> 00:03:44.260
punim škorpiona.

00:03:44.260 --> 00:03:47.260
I njihova ljubav [za studiranjem]

00:03:47.260 --> 00:03:52.260
je bila toliko velika da sam zaplakala.

00:03:52.260 --> 00:03:54.260
Što znamo

00:03:54.260 --> 00:03:57.260
o smrtnim prijetnjama Talibana

00:03:57.260 --> 00:03:59.260
naljepljenim na vrata

00:03:59.260 --> 00:04:05.260
ljudi koji su se usudili poslati svoje kćeri u školu kao u Balkhu?

00:04:05.260 --> 00:04:08.260
Regija nije sigurna, i puna je Talibana,

00:04:08.260 --> 00:04:10.260
ali su oni to učinili.

00:04:10.260 --> 00:04:12.260
Moj cilj je dati glas

00:04:12.260 --> 00:04:15.260
tihim ljudima,

00:04:15.260 --> 00:04:19.260
pokazati skriveno svjetlo

00:04:19.260 --> 00:04:22.260
iza zavjesa velike igre,

00:04:22.260 --> 00:04:25.260
malih svjetova koje mediji ignoriraju

00:04:25.260 --> 00:04:27.260
kao i propovjednici globalnog sukoba.

00:04:27.260 --> 00:04:29.260
Hvala.

00:04:29.260 --> 00:04:38.260
(Pljesak)

